My mom is 70 years old. in 2008 she had back surgery (L3-L5 fusion) and cannot work, but she is active. 2 years ago she wanted to move into my (large) house and said she would not interfere with my life, just live quietly. That has changed rather quickly. She does not pay any bills, never help me with mortgage, just helped me on few home improvements. I always tried to keep her happy, we went on many roadtrips, she saw more of America in last 2 years than her whole life. she  is not required to help me around house, as I can manage my self, but I did allow her to help me to keep her busy and occupied. She tries to control me, makes decisions for me, tells me what I can and cannot do in my life, in my house. When she is mad, she accuses me of stealing her things (that I would have no use for).  I cannot take this any more. She has money to move out, even to buy own condo, but would not help me with my bills. I know she's my mom, but the way she treats me is ridiculous.

Edit: this wasn't planned on being viral, this was supposed to be me venting in usersub... but thanks all for support.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UFcGJYy</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AloneInTheWoods]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Large Loud Husky Dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8rqgzrJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TdbMx1q.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love huskies. I love the husky videos. I thought I’d make a dump. MVEdit: send talking dogs & cats</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5QG27nu.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I do not want a husky however.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/13ruCo0.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I would not be a good husky mom.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Drdw5W1.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love how derpy they are. Edit: credit for this dreaming doggo to @theSilencewillfall</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2yVxTNx.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>How absolutely goofballs they are.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ARxuv8x.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But holy cow they are so loud.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jgTNzzB.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And argumentative.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QgQfTi3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And generally too smart. For me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/20ZMWAN.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My parents had a brush wolf / malamute when I was born.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LTE4o5K.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Her name was Tequila.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/b5kClLW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If I had a husky I would name in Moon Moon because I still laugh at that.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UlOb1Fw.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And also because I haven’t put much thought into naming a husky because I do not want a husky.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FGwCB14.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But I absolutely love & enjoy</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HW4fLtz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Videos of other peoples’ huskies.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/un7p3MT.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yLe7hZm.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So I thought</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ntln9i5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Maybe I’m not the only one.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hfEcz54.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And in these perpetually unprecedented for one reason or another times</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vyszfl2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Maybe a dump of huskies hollering, talking & being huskies</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jn3NMit.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Would be enjoyed by others as well.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CbaVdAM.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So here it is. I mean look at that hollering chonk.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kEhxYPe.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If I stole a video from you, thank you for sharing it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KR4gx1l.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It is appreciated.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CiaqK6L.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So conversational.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/X17PqdA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>These videos always crack me up.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LQaBpuv.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Also the ones of angry cats singing.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FkdgwqJ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Maybe if I lived alone</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0qhoTzv.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I could devote my life to one or two</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MWzT6D9.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Adorable.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/l037KXN.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But not in my current life.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/re3Y4bS.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wqAWfyl.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VFrOQ4W.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5YKELSE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VOphRHO.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JaU3tME.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QMLEzFA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FQXrYlE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That energy level omg</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/r8dy4HL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KQrHy5i.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GBRkhBV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vQ8g5q3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dfHTDMb.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/m0ABkTo.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CHdFnvT.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3C5rfk0.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eqacsbZ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tlHgx2a.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’ve probably spent 15 minutes of my life watching this and giggling. I have no idea why. It just makes me laugh.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wyDmVAf.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;">